    "// Hint: AtomicUsize::fetch_add(1, Ordering::Relaxed)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 🎯 Key Takeaways\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Middleware** = request/response pipeline layers (logging, CORS, auth, timing)\n",
    "2. `tower-http` provides CORS, Trace, and other common middleware\n",
    "3. Custom middleware: `middleware::from_fn(|req, next| next.run(req))`\n",
    "4. **State&lt;T&gt;** injects shared state; use `Router::with_state(state)`\n",
    "5. `Arc<RwLock<T>>` or `Arc<Mutex<T>>` for shared mutable state\n",
    "6. `Extension` vs `State`: Extension for per-layer injection, State for app-wide config\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "**Tomorrow:** Static files and templates! 📁"
   ]
